{
  "name": "Campaña Email Semanal - Rotación 4 Semanas",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "b2c3d4e5-0002-0002-0002-000000000001",
      "name": "Schedule Trigger Semanal",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.scheduleTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1.2,
      "position": [0, 300],
      "parameters": {
        "rule": {
          "interval": [
            {
              "field": "cronExpression",
              "expression": "0 8 * * 1"
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "b2c3d4e5-0002-0002-0002-000000000002",
      "name": "Calcular Semana del Ciclo",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [220, 300],
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const now = new Date();\nconst startOfYear = new Date(now.getFullYear(), 0, 1);\nconst weekOfYear = Math.ceil(((now - startOfYear) / 86400000 + startOfYear.getDay() + 1) / 7);\nconst weekCycle = ((weekOfYear - 1) % 4) + 1;\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    weekOfYear,\n    weekCycle,\n    date: now.toISOString().split('T')[0],\n    year: now.getFullYear()\n  }\n}];"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "b2c3d4e5-0002-0002-0002-000000000003",
      "name": "Switch Semana",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.switch",
      "typeVersion": 3,
      "position": [440, 300],
      "parameters": {
        "mode": "rules",
        "rules": {
          "rules": [
            {
              "conditions": {
                "conditions": [
                  {
                    "id": "rule-semana1",
                    "leftValue": "={{ $json.weekCycle }}",
                    "rightValue": 1,
                    "operator": {
                      "type": "number",
                      "operation": "equals"
                    }
                  }
                ],
                "combinator": "and"
              },
              "renameOutput": true,
              "outputKey": "Semana 1 - Cursos"
            },
            {
              "conditions": {
                "conditions": [
                  {
                    "id": "rule-semana2",
                    "leftValue": "={{ $json.weekCycle }}",
                    "rightValue": 2,
                    "operator": {
                      "type": "number",
                      "operation": "equals"
                    }
                  }
                ],
                "combinator": "and"
              },
              "renameOutput": true,
              "outputKey": "Semana 2 - Noticias"
            },
            {
              "conditions": {
                "conditions": [
                  {
                    "id": "rule-semana3",
                    "leftValue": "={{ $json.weekCycle }}",
                    "rightValue": 3,
                    "operator": {
                      "type": "number",
                      "operation": "equals"
                    }
                  }
                ],
                "combinator": "and"
              },
              "renameOutput": true,
              "outputKey": "Semana 3 - Sin envio"
            },
            {
              "conditions": {
                "conditions": [
                  {
                    "id": "rule-semana4",
                    "leftValue": "={{ $json.weekCycle }}",
                    "rightValue": 4,
                    "operator": {
                      "type": "number",
                      "operation": "equals"
                    }
                  }
                ],
                "combinator": "and"
              },
              "renameOutput": true,
              "outputKey": "Semana 4 - Precios"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "b2c3d4e5-0002-0002-0002-000000000004",
      "name": "Preparar Email Cursos",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.set",
      "typeVersion": 3.4,
      "position": [700, 80],
      "parameters": {
        "mode": "manual",
        "assignments": {
          "assignments": [
            {
              "id": "s1-subject",
              "name": "subject",
              "value": "=🎓 Cursos disponibles esta semana - {{ $('Calcular Semana del Ciclo').item.json.date }}",
              "type": "string"
            },
            {
              "id": "s1-body",
              "name": "body",
              "value": "<h2>Cursos Disponibles Esta Semana</h2><p>Estimado/a,</p><p>Te compartimos los cursos disponibles esta semana para potenciar tus habilidades profesionales:</p><ul><li><strong>Curso 1:</strong> Descripción del curso 1 - <a href='#'>Ver detalles</a></li><li><strong>Curso 2:</strong> Descripción del curso 2 - <a href='#'>Ver detalles</a></li><li><strong>Curso 3:</strong> Descripción del curso 3 - <a href='#'>Ver detalles</a></li></ul><p>Inscríbete ahora y obtén un <strong>10% de descuento</strong> usando el código: SEMANA01</p><p>Saludos,<br>El Equipo de Formación</p>",
              "type": "string"
            },
            {
              "id": "s1-week",
              "name": "weekType",
              "value": "cursos",
              "type": "string"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      }
    },
